{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0879a6ead","title":"给江青的几封信和批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"14ca374522","index":0,"year":1974,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"f0879a6ead"}],"tags":[{"id":"264b63d816","name":"四人帮","type":"主题"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"785fa02ecf","type":"title","text":"给江青的几封信和批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"960c5a7bcb","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"eacf63e3e4","type":"paragraph","text":"不见还好些。过去多年同你谈的，你有好些不执行，多见何益？有马列书在，有我的书在，你就是不研究。我重病在身，八十一了，也不体谅。你有特权，我死了，看你怎么办？你也是个大事不讨论，小事天天送的人。请你考虑。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"278e9c808c","type":"paragraph","text":"3. 20","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"86c83df054","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"3035e69f54","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平同志出国是我的意见，你不要反对为好。小心谨慎，不要反对我的提议。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"c0af400f3c","type":"paragraph","text":"3. 27","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"1df74bdf13","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"4169f7c58b","type":"paragraph","text":"两信收。前后不一。党的大势不错，悲观不好。不要动摇。前途是光明的，道路是曲折的。要团结百分之九十五以上的人。不要主观片观（面）。千万注意。牢骚太盛防肠断，风物长宜（放）眼量。不要请假。钱可略增。无限风光在险峰。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"503c7f81dc","type":"paragraph","text":"4. 17","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"db5dc5fd3b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"23c9f72af5","type":"paragraph","text":"可读李固给黄琼书。就思想文章而论，都是一篇好文章。你的职务就是研究国内外动态，这已经是大任务了。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"8996b99025","type":"paragraph","text":"此事我对你说了多次，不要说没有工作。此嘱。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"},{"id":"3db1284352","type":"paragraph","text":"11. 20","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead"}],"page":{"id":"cea3d00753","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f0879a6ead","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}